_header: At sometime merry at some time sad
_description: James Ryman, The Transitoriness of this World — eight 8-line stanzas

CULEe112.First Lines:
Atte sumtyme mery at summe tyme saddeAt suntyme wele at sumtyme
                    woo…
CULEe112.Last Lines:
…Whoes Ioye no tunge canne comprehendeThat ay shall be is
                    & ay wace
